|---|---|---|
| 🔴 1 | No auth on `/users` | Add JWT/session middleware |
| 🔴 2 | PII exposure | Restrict fields by role |
| 🟠 3 | No security headers | `helmet()` |
| 🟠 4 | No rate limiting | `express-rate-limit` |
| 🟠 5 | No CORS policy | `cors()` with allowlist |
| 🟡 6 | No error handler | Global `(err, req, res, next)` handler |
| 🟡 7 | No body size limits | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| 🟡 8 | No HTTPS | Redirect or proxy enforcement |

